{"tid":176138,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣漫畫大師鄭問離世","createTime":"2017-03-28T03:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T05:59:22.000Z","uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43bd317da490f4c42e62e10830215704a25476de","tid":176138,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:49:57.000Z","msg":"著有《刺客列傳》等作品的台灣著名漫畫家鄭問（原名鄭進文）於3月26日因心肌梗塞離世，享年58歲。<br />\n<br />\n鄭問的弟子鍾孟舜等人在臉書公告，鄭問於3月26日心肌梗塞過世。鄭問弟子指出，鄭問過身非常祥和，「走時非常祥和，有如他武林神話一般風格。」<br />\n<br />\n鄭問在1991年獲日本漫畫家協會頒發「優秀賞」，是該獎二十年來第一位非日籍的得獎者。<br />\n<br />\n鄭問1958年出生，1984年在發表首部作品《戰士黑豹》而展開漫畫生涯，創作多基於歷史、武俠故事，著名作品有《東周英雄傳》、《刺客列傳》、《阿鼻劍》等。2002年，他曾與香港漫畫家馬榮成推出全彩手繪漫畫《風雲外傳：天下無雙》。"},{"pid":"a2e76dc974a92798322e2ed2dba35c038624b41d","tid":176138,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一路好走"},{"pid":"0c88742d0ef6b87620e6123ce6566414dd6425d4","tid":176138,"uid":73404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:07:36.000Z","msg":"東周英雄傳好撚好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818e3ebf57a0cf50c71ad70785b24e23a21e5b50","tid":176138,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"咁突然"},{"pid":"882a1aefe9fe138047a807a69bd3af2e24bed9b2","tid":176138,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:26:33.000Z","msg":"又一個大師離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50bd096fc88d13b36da132af90b8ce7af343b3a","tid":176138,"uid":25002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:38:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a65fde56c2a88a3f947acacd8653b89d748bda80","tid":176138,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:11:48.000Z","msg":"台灣井上"},{"pid":"516dd2